videos.description: Lamontray Harris  cleans up the missed shot by flushing a two-handed dunk over a UConn defender.
videos.headline: Harris cleans up  miss with two-handed stuff

videos.description: Tarin Smith goes baseline and rises up for the strong flush over a Morhead defender.
videos.headline: Smith throws down baseline slam over defender

videos.description: Morehead's Malek Green poses after knocking down a 3 before the buzzer at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Green drains first half buzzer-beating 3

videos.description: UConn's Jalen Adams throws a pinpoint bounce pass to Tarin Smith on the fast break for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Adams throws slick bounce pass to Smith on break

videos.description: Josh Carlton receives the entry pass and uses a drop step to throw down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Carlton utilizes drop step to dunk on defender
